	"system": {
		"description": "<p>You are learned even by the standards of other wizards, with a breadth and depth of magical knowledge that makes you like unto a mage school personified. You gain the following benefits:</p><ul><li><p>Your Dexterity, Wisdom, or Intelligence score increases by +1, to a maximum of 20.</p></li><li><p>You learn an additional @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.1u4hyjbgjmvl22js]{Elective Study}.</p></li><li><p>You learn two additional cantrips from the wizard spell list.</p></li><li><p>You learn three wizard spells of up to 6th level.</p></li><li><p>You can prepare an additional number of spells per day equal to half your proficiency bonus.</p></li><li><p>The gp and time costs to research rare spells are reduced by 50% for you (this improves the discount from the previous feat, but does not stack with it).</p></li></ul><p>Once you have selected this feat, you can no longer gain levels in classes other than wizard.</p>",
